Name:                snapper
Version:             0.1
Synopsis:            Sinatra workalike on Snap framework
Description:         Project Description Here
License:             PublicDomain
Author:              Audrey Tang
Maintainer:          Audrey Tang <audreyt@audreyt.org>
Stability:           Experimental
Category:            Web
Build-type:          Simple
Cabal-version:       >= 1.2
Tested-With:         GHC==6.10.1, GHC==7.0.2

Source-Repository head
    type: git
    location: git://github.com/audreyt/snapper.git

